---
title: "A) ROGUE_CO - Client Authentication Failures"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant CO as Rogue CO
    participant SP as Service Provider
    
    CO->>SP: mTLS Connection Attempt
    
    alt MISSING Certificate
        SP-->>CO: TLS Alert: peer not authenticated
        Note right of SP: No client cert in handshake
    else SELF_SIGNED Certificate
        SP-->>CO: TLS Alert: PKIX validation failed
        Note right of SP: Cert not signed by trusted CA
    end
    
    Note over CO,SP: Connection terminated<br/>No application data exchanged
